title: Goyard Plumet Pocket Wallet Crossbody Bag
description: Goyard Plumet pocket wallet crossbody bag in white Goyardine Canvas & Chevroches Calfskin. Featuring silver-toned hardware, exterior rear patch pocket, and flap with snap button fastening. This opens to a beige textile interior with three compartments with card slots. Approximate dimensions: 21cm(L) x 14cm(H) x 2cm(D), strap drop 55cm. Accompanied by Goyard dustbag and tag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
